        <mxCell id="0gpFdqcg0QWsmTuHOBDj-2" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="Design an Instagram like system with the following requirements:&lt;div&gt;1.User Login Service&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2. Content Service&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3. Feed Service&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4. Follower Service&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;5. User Engagement Service&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Implement a mechanism to restrict the user for posting a non - policy complaint post.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Optimize the dynamic feed generation for the users&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Highlight Backfill.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="700" x="60" y="70" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="0gpFdqcg0QWsmTuHOBDj-3" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;h2&gt;Functional Requirements:&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div&gt;1. User Should be able to register and login.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2. User should be able to post photos, videos and other media.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3. User can like, unlike and comment on other posts.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4. User can follow and unfollow other users.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;5. User should be able to view their feed and interact with the contents.&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="620" x="80" y="210" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="0gpFdqcg0QWsmTuHOBDj-4" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;h2&gt;Non-Functional Requirements:&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div&gt;1.Low Latency.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2. High availability: 99.9 percent.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3. Highly Scalable : should be able to handle upto 1.5 Billion daily users.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4. High Throughput.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="520" x="165" y="330" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
